Zhao Xinfang wore light makeup that accentuated her large, bright almond-shaped eyes. Though it was already late autumn, she was dressed in a pure white spaghetti-strap dress. The deliberately lowered neckline failed to conceal the deep valley of her cleavage, and her long, fair legs were positioned suggestively, making her figure appear even more alluring.

