Wei Xiyan’s parents had left him a vast inheritance—though it couldn’t compare to the Ning family’s fortune, it was more than enough for an ordinary person to live in luxury for several lifetimes. Zhao Xinfang had thought long and hard before deciding to make him one of her conquests, someone she could use.

Men, like women, never forget their first time. And she intended to be Wei Xiyan’s first.

